sequenceDiagram
    actor Client
    participant PEP
    participant PDP
    participant PIP
    participant PAP

    Note over PDP,PAP: Pro-active (outside the trace)
    PAP-->>PDP: Distribute policies
    PIP-->>PDP: Pre-populate static information

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
    Note over Client,PIP: Trace
    Client->>+PEP: Request
    rect rgb(205, 220, 245)
    Note over PEP,PDP: Sub-span: PEP → PDP
    PEP->>+PDP: Access Evaluation Request
    rect rgb(180, 200, 235)
    Note over PDP,PIP: Sub-span: PDP → PIP
    PDP->>+PIP: Query dynamic information
    PIP-->>-PDP: Response
    end
    PDP->>PDP: Decide
    PDP->>-PEP: Decision
    end
    PEP-->>-Client: Response
    end
